		{
			description: [
				"The world is scarred. Lost."
				""
				"Years have passed since the loss of &l&eThe Ultimate Zookeeper&r&r, but the wounds have not healed."
				""
				"It is up to you. You must bring back &l&eThe Ultimate Zookeeper&r&r. And to do that, you will have to become &eThe Penultimate Zookeeper&r."
				""
				"Travel the world. Gather its creatures. Learn their secrets. Gain their strength. Save the Zookeeper, save the world."
