			description: [
				""
				"It's dangerous to go alone! Take this."
				""
				"He is a &aMantis Shrimp&r. Tame him with &9marine food&r or &9tropical fish&r and he will be your first friend of many."
				""
				"He can follow you around, and will even fight off enemies. But his real strength lies in his block-breaking ability. Just put him in &6Break Blocks&r mode, and then hand him the block to break with shift+right click!"
				""
				"Keep in mind that he can only breathe in the water. If you lose him, you can buy more from a pet store in a village, or catch one in the wild in reefs or mangrove swamps."
			]
			icon: {
				Count: 1
